data.description: Check out this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home, quiet setting on 1 acre just south of Big Rapids.  Home features an open floor plan, Large walk out deck in the back, with a perfect view nature.  Plenty of room in the 2 stall attached garage.  Full walk out basement with sliding glass doors. Basement is ready to be finished to your liking along with a possible third bathroom.   Call today to set up your showing.
